
## **4. Elementary Statistics & Probability**  
### **Key Concepts:**  
- **Mean, Median, Mode**  
- **Standard Deviation (σ)** = `√(Σ(xᵢ - μ)²/N)`  
- **Probability Rules:**  
  - `P(A∪B) = P(A) + P(B) - P(A∩B)`  
  - **Bayes’ Theorem**: `P(A|B) = [P(B|A)*P(A)] / P(B)`  

